---
title: Classic Turkey Meatballs with Spaghetti and Parmesan
description: Our spaghetti and meatballs tastes just like Nonna's, but takes a fraction of the time! The secret to these leaner meatballs is swapping ground beef for turkey and pairing with a homemade tomato sauce that keeps the dish flavourful.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-dinde-classiques-a72c30b0.jpg
